{
  "stem": "24242.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There weren't any-- there were no rapes in our area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In other words, in the Bielski brigade, there were no rapes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If a woman wanted to be with him, to sleep with him, that's her business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But if she turned him down, he wouldn't force her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was unacceptable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And don't forget, this is wartime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, those are people with minds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They know it's wartime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If, if the rule is don't go force anybody to do anything, I mean, there was rules and regulations.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You better live by that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because a person's life means nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were, yes, the very tough ones, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did jokes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] would get drunk sometimes, you know, and--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said, it was needed very little, discipline.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All you had to be is told.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whoever is-- by your commander, whoever is in charge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it's Pesach's group or if it's anybody else's group, he will tell him, look, this is unacceptable.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Don't do this no more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because if it will get to my brothers, you'll be in trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there is, there was very little punishment there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Punishment is a bullet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so, a lot of drinking, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Without the alcohol, I don't think they would be able to-- see, as depends how much alcohol a person takes in and how he can handle, how much alcohol he can handle.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Alcohol at times is very good, [BACKGROUND NOISE] very helpful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of drinking was, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was disagreements, as I told you before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went and wrote in a letter to the high Russian command that my brothers did wrong things, were doing wrong things.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
